With CRRA utility:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
c_{0}: & R=\frac{\left(c_{1}^{y}\right)^{\sigma}}{\beta\left(c_{0}\right)^{\sigma}}+-\sigma\left(c_{0}\right)^{-\sigma-1}\frac{k}{\lambda_{1}\theta}\mu-\left(c_{0}+k\right)^{-\sigma}\frac{\phi}{\lambda_{1}}\\
